title: Spacious 1 bedroom + den, 1 bath with unbeatable bay view
posting_body: ['%&$%Spacious 1 bedroom + den, 1 bath with unbeatable bay, city and brickell view.', 'Gorgeous Italian kitchen includes stainless steel appliances with double thick granite countertop, tile floors throughout, washer and dryer inside the unit.', 'Luxury condominium on the Miami River features 2 floors of amenities including: infinity pool, sauna, theater, meditation garden, billiard, party room with kitchen, 24 hours concierge, 24 hours security and management on-site.', 'Excellent location only a few minutes from downtown, brickell, tennis club and very brickell village.%&$&', '#$%If you have been denied an application for lease in the past due to bad credit or your background, please call me or text me', 'show contact info', ', I will get you approved!!', 'Self-employed, bad credit, no problem.', 'Text me, I respond immediately and have tons of inventory!', 'WE ARE ESSENTIAL BUSINESS FOR COVI19, WE ARE ALWAYS OPEN', 'CALL ME OR TEXT ME', 'Andy Zamudio', 'show contact info', 'We accept deposits with credit card if you are short of cash we help with that, we are the only company that accepts credit cards for deposits , zelle, cash app, paypal venmo payments accepted!!!', 'Aceptamos los depositos con tarjeta de credito sinud esta corto de cash, somos la unica compañia que lo acepta en Florida, zelle, cash app, paypal ,venmo.']
